  "instructions": [
    "This is a Flutter application using go_router for navigation and Provider for state management.",
    "Bottom tabs: Home | My Appointments | Health Record | My Account.",
    "For QR codes in prescriptions, use the qr_flutter package.",
    "The UI should look calm, organic, and trustworthy — use generous padding (24px on containers) and the specified warm color palette.",
    "The Home dashboard has a dynamic smart widget: if there is an upcoming appointment, show the dark green (#2A433A) contextual card at the top; otherwise show the welcome card.",
